            <title>[WICKET-5582] ServletWebResponse#encodeUrl() makes absolute Urls relative</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5582</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When an absolute (full) URL is passed to ServletWebResponse#encodeUrl(), it will be returned relative if the container encodes a session ID.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
